# 7.10 Streamable HTTP

Google Maps and Tavily use

```
StreamableHTTPConnectionParams
```

Example

```python
StreamableHTTPConnectionParams(
    url="https://..."
)
```

Advantages

- Streaming responses
- Better scalability
- Lower latency
- Standard HTTP infrastructure

