# 7.11 STDIO Communication

Local MCP servers communicate using

```
Standard Input

↓

Standard Output
```

Example

```python
StdioConnectionParams(
    server_params=...
)
```

The AI application launches the MCP server as a child process.

Communication happens through pipes.

This makes STDIO ideal for local tools.

